 
<p>

  US citizens: <a href="https://actionnetwork.org/forms/sign-the-petition-dont-militarize-our-schools">oppose flooding schools with guns and uniformed thugs</a>.
<p>
The special danger of <a class=glossary href="/glossary.html#thug">thugs</a> in schools is that they can direct
students into the <a href="https://stallman.org/archives/2013-nov-feb.html#11_January_2014_('Groundbreaking'_Guidelines_to_Stop_'School-to-Prison_Pipeline">school-to-prison pipeline</a>.  They do this
for minor matters of indiscipline that in the past would not have
involved the state at all.

 